GOOD expansion of "patient on metformin 500mg":
"Patient currently prescribed metformin hydrochloride 500 milligrams, an
oral antihyperglycemic agent of the biguanide class, for management of
diabetes mellitus."

BAD expansion of "patient on metformin 500mg":
"Patient on metformin 500mg with monitoring of renal function, HbA1c,
hepatic function, and risk of lactic acidosis."
(This adds monitoring/complications — the query only mentions the medication.)

User Input: {query}
"""


